                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9315" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0276</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1239 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">循“智”而治，无为无不为 ——黄陵矿业智慧纪检降本增效之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">To govern according to &quot;wisdom&quot;, to do everything without exception——The Road of Intelligent Discipline Inspection in Huangling Mining to Reduce Costs and Increase Efficiency</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">冯英，潘新兴，梁思瑶，狄雨润，侯馨月</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西陕煤黄陵矿业有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">监察与纪检部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">21 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">智慧纪检；公司治理；降本增效；风险管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Smart disciplinary inspection; Corporate governance; Reduce costs and increase efficiency; Risk management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着煤炭产业的发展，陕煤集团核心骨干企业——黄陵矿业公司的发展蒸蒸日上，企业体量逐渐壮大，产业链条不断延长，项目及物资采购等方面涉及资金量持续放大，企业的管控难度和公职人员廉洁风险也随之增大。为了强化项目资金和权力管控，避免不当履职，确保权力运行在控、可控，黄陵矿业公司纪委创建了一个“事前提醒、事中监督再提醒、事后评价分析追溯”的集团化监控、平台化运行的数字纪检监督平台，企业分别从“业务流程系统管理、适时智能提醒预警、数据可视化分析、系统平台管理”四个方面有效地对各项工程项目、物资采购以及选人用人等权力资金运行和审批流程进行适时监督提醒，规范了履职行为，降低了管理成本，管控了廉洁风险。本案例希望能为广大国有企业内部监管治理方面提供参考，同时结合具体案例，可以使学生深度理解中国式公司治理模式和特点，信息系统的迭代升级以及精细化管理理论等相关知识。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the development of the coal industry, Huangling Mining Company, the core backbone enterprise of Shaanxi Coal Group, is thriving. The enterprise size is gradually expanding, the industrial chain is continuously extending, and the amount of funds involved in project and material procurement continues to increase. The difficulty of enterprise control and the risk of integrity of public officials are also increasing. In order to strengthen the control of project funds and power, avoid improper performance of duties, and ensure the operation of power is under control and controllable, the Discipline Inspection Commission of Huangling Mining Company has created a group based monitoring and platform based digital disciplinary supervision platform with &quot;prior reminders, in-process supervision and reminders, and post evaluation analysis and tracing&quot;. The enterprise has effectively supervised and reminded the operation and approval process of power funds for various engineering projects, material procurement, and personnel selection and use from four aspects: business process system management, timely intelligent reminders and warnings, data visualization analysis, and system platform management, standardizing performance behavior, reducing management costs, and controlling integrity risks. This case study aims to provide reference for the internal regulatory governance of state-owned enterprises, and combined with specific cases, it can help students deeply understand the Chinese style corporate governance model and characteristics, the iterative upgrading of information systems, and the theory of refined management.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字赋能理论；委托代理理论；精细化管理理论；风险管理理论；中国式公司治理模式和特点</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-02</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
